name: Ma-Crab
description:
An innocent crab? Is that really ketchup? What happens when the "food" decides to fight back?

Haha! This was a play on words between "macabre" and "crab" 
Macabre meaning disturbing and a crab bc it's kind of ironic. I was playing around with vectors and colored it in Procreate on ipad. I really love the detail of the skin and the bluish lips. I like using vectors bc of the crisp lines and curves

2048x2048 px
created in September bc I was thinking about Halloween 
Follow me on my artistic adventure @yoXneo
